      "title": "[DC] morimensstaff06@🔸官方素材┊official-materials: 感谢各位守密人的支持！ 《忘却前夜》新OST已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。 如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商",
      "summary": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》新OST已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处**\n有一种叫蒲公英的植物，会让种子乘着风漂流。\n毛绒绒的种子随风流浪，离开故土好远好远。\n它孤身一人，会在什么时候决定自己的归宿呢？\n那就是，沙漠中有唯一的一个人爱着那株蒲公英的时候。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n企划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens new OST was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens × Saya no Uta OST┊Saya EP: Where the Dandelions Go**\nThere is a plant called the dandelion, which lets its seeds drift away upon the wind.\nThe downy seeds wander wherever the wind carries them, far, so very far from the soil that bore them.\nWhen does such a lonely seed decide where it belongs?\n...It is the moment when, somewhere in the desert, one single person happens to love that dandelion.\n\nProject: B.I.A.V. Studio\nComposer: F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n[附件: c8bbaf0adc87f25e.png]",
